Bio:

 Razakel first picked up the mic in January 2006 and has developed a very strong and loyal underground following as the Queen of the Wicked Shit. Early in 2006 Razakel got involved with other underground artists and got "signed" to a label that has since folded. In mid 2006 Razakel was contacted by Serial Killin Records for a possible contract, a demo was exchanged and a meeting arranged.
